        "subject": "LU-6730 tests: fix fail_loc code in conf-sanity test 45",
        "message": "LU-6730 tests: fix fail_loc code in conf-sanity test 45\n\nThis patch fixes the fail_loc code in conf-sanity test 45 to\nOR with the OBD_FAIL_ONCE (0x80000000) to prevent\nthe fail_loc from looping forever.\n\nIt also fixes the fail_loc code name from\nOBD_FAIL_PTLRPC_LONG_UNLINK to\nOBD_FAIL_PTLRPC_LONG_REPL_UNLINK.\n\nTest-Parameters: alwaysuploadlogs envdefinitions=ONLY=45 \\\nmdtfilesystemtype=ldiskfs mdsfilesystemtype=ldiskfs ostfilesystemtype=ldiskfs \\\nclientdistro=el6.6 ossdistro=el6.6 mdsdistro=el6.6 \\\nmdtcount=1 testlist=conf-sanity\n\nTest-Parameters: alwaysuploadlogs envdefinitions=ONLY=45 \\\nmdtfilesystemtype=zfs mdsfilesystemtype=zfs ostfilesystemtype=zfs \\\nclientdistro=el6.6 ossdistro=el6.6 mdsdistro=el6.6 \\\nmdtcount=1 testlist=conf-sanity\n\nSigned-off-by: Jian Yu <jian.yu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I347a88d36bc75e297a1d78f274b78f9b930b15c1\n"
